SELECT job_id, job_name, assigned_resource FROM printing_jobs WHERE job_status = 'Pending' ORDER BY scheduled_time ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT job_name, job_priority, scheduled_time FROM printing_jobs WHERE job_priority BETWEEN 3 AND 7 ORDER BY scheduled_time DESC

SELECT job_id, job_name, priority FROM PrintingJobs WHERE priority > 5 ORDER BY priority DESC;
SELECT r.resource_name, r.status, p.job_name FROM Resources r INNER JOIN PrintingJobs p ON r.resource_id = p.job_id;

SELECT job_name, resources_required FROM PrintingJobs ORDER BY resources_required DESC;

SELECT job_name, resource_name, start_time, end_time FROM PrintingJobs INNER JOIN JobSchedule ON PrintingJobs.job_id = JobSchedule.job_id INNER JOIN Resources ON JobSchedule.resource_id = Resources.resource_id;

SELECT job_name, status, availability FROM PrintingJobs JOIN JobSchedule ON PrintingJobs.job_id = JobSchedule.job_id JOIN Resources ON JobSchedule.resource_id = Resources.resource_id WHERE status='pending' AND availability='available';
SELECT * FROM JobSchedule js JOIN PrintingJobs pj ON js.job_id = pj.job_id JOIN Resources r ON js.resource_id = r.resource_id WHERE pj.status = 'printing'
SELECT job_id, job_name, priority FROM PrintingJobs WHERE priority > 3 ORDER BY job_id DESC
SELECT * FROM Resources WHERE availability = 'available' AND resource_name LIKE '%paper%'
SELECT job_id, job_name, status, resources_required FROM PrintingJobs WHERE status IN ('pending', 'printing')

SELECT pj.job_name, r.resource_name, js.start_time, js.end_time FROM JobSchedule js JOIN PrintingJobs pj ON js.job_id = pj.job_id JOIN Resources r ON js.resource_id = r.resource_id WHERE js.start_time > '2022-10-01'

SELECT job_name, status FROM PrintingJobs WHERE status = 'Pending';

SELECT job_id, scheduled_date FROM JobSchedule WHERE scheduled_date >= NOW();
SELECT * FROM PrintingJobs INNER JOIN JobSchedule ON PrintingJobs.job_id = JobSchedule.job_id;
SELECT job_id, job_name, priority, status FROM PrintingJobs WHERE priority > 5 ORDER BY priority ASC;

SELECT PrintingJobs.job_id, PrintingJobs.job_name, JobSchedule.resource_id, JobSchedule.scheduled_date FROM PrintingJobs LEFT JOIN JobSchedule ON PrintingJobs.job_id = JobSchedule.job_id WHERE JobSchedule.scheduled_date >= '2022-10-01';
SELECT resource_name, available_quantity FROM Resources WHERE available_quantity < 10 ORDER BY available_quantity DESC;

SELECT PrintingJobs.job_id, PrintingJobs.job_name, JobHistory.start_time, JobHistory.end_time FROM PrintingJobs INNER JOIN JobHistory ON PrintingJobs.job_id = JobHistory.job_id WHERE JobHistory.start_time > '2022-09-01';
